<h2>Government Resources</h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://www.consumerfinance.gov/">Consumer Financial Protection Bureau</a> (CFPB) - file complaints about financial services</li>
<li><a href="https://www.ftc.gov/">Federal Trade Commission</a> - consumer protection, FDCPA violations</li>
<li><a href="https://www.uscourts.gov/services-forms/bankruptcy">U.S. Courts Bankruptcy Resources</a> - official forms and court locator</li>
<li><a href="https://www.usdoj.gov/ust/">U.S. Trustee Program</a> - federal bankruptcy oversight</li>
<li><a href="https://www.fjc.gov/research/idb">FJC Integrated Database</a> - federal court case statistics</li>
</ul>
<h2>Primary Law</h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://www.law.cornell.edu/uscode/text/11">Title 11 U.S. Code (Bankruptcy)</a> - Cornell Law</li>
<li><a href="https://www.law.cornell.edu/uscode/text/15/chapter-41">Title 15 Chapter 41 (FDCPA, FCRA, TILA)</a> - Cornell Law</li>
</ul>
